---
title: AI Assistant Workflow
---

flowchart LR
    A[User prompt] --> B[Understand request]
    B --> C{Planning needed?}
    C -- Yes --> D[Plan tasks]
    C -- No --> E[Delegate work]
    D --> E
    E --> F[Gather agent feedback]
    G --> E
    F --> G[Revise if needed]
    G --> H[Return final response]